message: “People don’t want to talk about sex trafficking,” Ranck said. “When we’re talking about the victimization of young people and women, it’s just hard to think that there’s people in the world like this, but it’s not going to go away if we don’t acknowledge this.”

data.description: On Saturday, Brenda Long is coming home to Newton with a message she wants to share with the community.
data.title: Anti Human Trafficking Advocates fight to raise awareness
